```plantuml
@startuml aws-solutions_iot-device-simulator

actor User

participant "GUI-Based Engine" as GUI
participant "Device Type Manager" as DTM
participant "Simulation Manager" as SM
participant "Simulator" as Simulator
participant "AWS IoT Core" as IoT
participant "AWS Step Functions" as ASF
participant "AWS Services" as AWS

User -> GUI: Create new simulation
GUI -> DTM: Define device types
DTM -> Simulator: Initialize device instances
User -> GUI: Start simulation
GUI -> SM: Start simulation request
SM -> ASF: Trigger simulation workflow
ASF -> Simulator: Start device data generation
Simulator -> IoT: Send simulated data
IoT -> AWS: Forward data for further processing
User -> GUI: Stop simulation
GUI -> SM: Stop simulation request
SM -> ASF: Stop simulation workflow

@enduml
```